<h3>Question 11</h3>
<div><p><p>Discuss the characteristics of multimedia.</p</p></div><div><strong>Answer:</strong><br><style>body .mathjax_wrap{width: 100%;overflow-x: scroll;margin-bottom:10px;}</style><p>A Multimedia system has four basic characteristics:</p>
<ul style="list-style-type: square;">
<li>Multimedia systems must be <em>computer controlled</em>.</li>
<li>Multimedia systems are <em>integrated</em>.</li>
<li>The information they handle must be represented <em>digitally</em>.</li>
<li>The interface to the final presentation of media is usually <em>interactive</em>.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<h3>Question 12</h3>
<div><p><p>What is database system? How data can be stored using relational model.</p</p></div><div><strong>Answer:</strong><br><style>body .mathjax_wrap{width: 100%;overflow-x: scroll;margin-bottom:10px;}</style><p>Database system is the software package for managing the databases. There are several database systems on the basis of how they manage the database.</p>
<p>There are mainly two types of database forms</p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal;">
<li>Single-file Database</li>
<li>Relational Database</li>
</ol>
</div>
